{"word":"H2026 - הָרַג - hârag - haw-rag' - Destroy","slug":"H2026","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">הָרַג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hârag"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>haw-rag'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Destroy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D4;&#x05E8;&#x05D2; - ha&#x0302;rag</b> - <i>haw-rag'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>smite</i> with deadly intent: - destroy, out of hand, kill, murder (-er), put to [death], make [slaughter], slay (-er), X surely."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2027\">H2027</a>, <a href=\"#/H2028\">H2028</a>"}]}